short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Navigate through your tabs with ease with a Vim-like tab jump list

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tab Jump List is an open-source project that brings the power of Vim-style navigation to your browser tabs. Seamlessly move back and forward through your tab history, all with simple keyboard shortcuts.

To go back to the last opened tab: Ctrl + o
To go forward in time: Ctrl + i

These shorcuts can be configured in the Chrome extension keyboard shortcuts at: chrome://extensions
